ed buildings in the provincial capital of Chengdu, 70 miles to the east.</p><p>The provincial news office said the quake was felt in neighbouring provinces.</p><p>The epicentre lies along the same Longmenshan fault where <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/may/24/china.chinaearthquake\" title=\"\">the devastating 7.9-magnitude quake struck in May 2008</a>, leaving more than 90,000 people dead or missing and presumed dead.</p><div class=\"related\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/earthquakes\">Earthquakes</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/china\">China</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/natural-disasters\">Natural disasters and extreme weather</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/asia-pacific\">Asia Pacific</a></li></ul></div><br/><div class=\"terms\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk\">guardian.co.uk</a> &copy; 2013 Guardian News and Media Limited or its affiliated companies. All rights reserved. | Use of this content is subject to our <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/terms-of-service\">Terms & Conditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/feeds\">More Feeds</a></div><p style=\"clear:both\" />" "http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/apr/20/earthquake-china-sichuan-province" (20849 63736) new 21 nil nil ((title nil "Earthquake hits China's Sichuan province") (link nil "http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/apr/20/earthquake-china-sichuan-province") (description nil "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/91927?ns=guardian&pageName=Article%3Aearthquake-china-sichuan-province%3A1896834&ch=World+news&c3=GU.co.uk&c4=Earthquakes+%28News%29%2CChina+%28News%29%2CNatural+disasters+and+extreme+weather+%28News%29%2CWorld+news%2CAsia+Pacific+%28News%29&c5=Unclassified%2CNot+commercially+useful%2CCharities&c6=Associated+Press+in+Beijing&c7=2013%2F04%2F20